{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"鹊巢小筑","author":"Sean"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"9e915e82-2e82-5b14-a07d-2a760f36c48a","excerpt":"几个 inline 元素排列在一起的时候，它们之间会留有空白，这些空白往往不是我们想要的结果，今天我们来看看几个去掉 inline 元素留白的方法。 假设我们要写一个水平方向的菜单，每个菜单宽度一样，占满屏幕的宽度。我打算用 和数个 元素实现这个目的，html 和 CSS…","html":"<p>几个 inline 元素排列在一起的时候，它们之间会留有空白，这些空白往往不是我们想要的结果，今天我们来看看几个去掉 inline 元素留白的方法。</p>\n<p>假设我们要写一个水平方向的菜单，每个菜单宽度一样，占满屏幕的宽度。我打算用<code class=\"language-text\">ul</code>和数个<code class=\"language-text\">li</code>元素实现这个目的，html 和 CSS 的代码如下:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-html line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>ul</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>menu<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>li</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>menu__item<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>菜单1<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>li</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>menu__item<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>菜单2<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>li</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>menu__item<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>菜单3<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>li</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>menu__item<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>菜单4<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>li</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>menu__item<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>菜单5<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>ul</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-css line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token selector\">*,\n*::before,\n*::after</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">padding</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 0<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">margin</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 0<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">box-sizing</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> inherit<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token selector\">:root</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">font-size</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 62.5%<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">box-sizing</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> border-box<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token selector\">.menu</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">list-style</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> none<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token selector\">.menu__item</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">font-size</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 2rem<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">display</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> inline-block<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">width</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 20%<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">background-color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> lightcoral<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<p>结果并不是我希望的目录刚好占一行，并且每个元素的宽度是百分之 25，但是每个目录中间有一点空白区域，正是因为这些空白区域，最后一个菜单因为宽度不够，自动移到了下一行。</p>\n<p>\n  <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/1194efff0790689f6b37e716b91180ce/6f768/img-1.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 590px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 6.324110671936759%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAABQAAAABCAIAAABR8BlyAAAACXBIWXMAAAsSAAALEgHS3X78AAAAO0lEQVQI12O4PWPGt2XLvi5d+nnFiteHD/84dernqVNA8vWRIz9OnoSw38DYP0+f/vf1638g+PcPSAAAyW4y8wlYli4AAAAASUVORK5CYII='); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"image1\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/1194efff0790689f6b37e716b91180ce/b9e4f/img-1.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/1194efff0790689f6b37e716b91180ce/cf440/img-1.png 148w,\n/static/1194efff0790689f6b37e716b91180ce/d2d38/img-1.png 295w,\n/static/1194efff0790689f6b37e716b91180ce/b9e4f/img-1.png 590w,\n/static/1194efff0790689f6b37e716b91180ce/f9b6a/img-1.png 885w,\n/static/1194efff0790689f6b37e716b91180ce/2d849/img-1.png 1180w,\n/static/1194efff0790689f6b37e716b91180ce/bbefa/img-1.png 1770w,\n/static/1194efff0790689f6b37e716b91180ce/6f768/img-1.png 2530w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    \n图 1</p>\n<p>解决这个问题有四种方法，每一种方法都不是完美的方法，比较好的解决方法会在文章最后给出。</p>\n<h5>移除元素间的空白</h5>\n<p>产生空白的原因是，元素之间有换行符、空格、或是几个 tab，所以可以利用这个原理去掉空白。将上面的<code class=\"language-text\">html</code>代码做出下的改变:</p>\n<p>\n  <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/c2e929ccf89156bad377b35ea4c52209/8ee24/img-2.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 590px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 37.12984054669704%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"image2\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/c2e929ccf89156bad377b35ea4c52209/b9e4f/img-2.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/c2e929ccf89156bad377b35ea4c52209/cf440/img-2.png 148w,\n/static/c2e929ccf89156bad377b35ea4c52209/d2d38/img-2.png 295w,\n/static/c2e929ccf89156bad377b35ea4c52209/b9e4f/img-2.png 590w,\n/static/c2e929ccf89156bad377b35ea4c52209/8ee24/img-2.png 878w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    \n或者\n\n  <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/b2a3b11ec9b803b4cb671e1e6adeb1d5/8ee24/img-3.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 590px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 37.12984054669704%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"image3\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/b2a3b11ec9b803b4cb671e1e6adeb1d5/b9e4f/img-3.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/b2a3b11ec9b803b4cb671e1e6adeb1d5/cf440/img-3.png 148w,\n/static/b2a3b11ec9b803b4cb671e1e6adeb1d5/d2d38/img-3.png 295w,\n/static/b2a3b11ec9b803b4cb671e1e6adeb1d5/b9e4f/img-3.png 590w,\n/static/b2a3b11ec9b803b4cb671e1e6adeb1d5/8ee24/img-3.png 878w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    \n再或者\n\n  <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/070cf0f055dba2a9b4608cd5067ceb4f/8ee24/img-4.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 590px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 37.12984054669704%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"image4\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/070cf0f055dba2a9b4608cd5067ceb4f/b9e4f/img-4.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/070cf0f055dba2a9b4608cd5067ceb4f/cf440/img-4.png 148w,\n/static/070cf0f055dba2a9b4608cd5067ceb4f/d2d38/img-4.png 295w,\n/static/070cf0f055dba2a9b4608cd5067ceb4f/b9e4f/img-4.png 590w,\n/static/070cf0f055dba2a9b4608cd5067ceb4f/8ee24/img-4.png 878w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    </p>\n<p>\n  <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/bf04d0bd9d87f3262e88d137360212d3/f8b3c/img-5.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 590px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 8.720112517580873%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAABQAAAACCAIAAADXZGvcAAAACXBIWXMAAAsSAAALEgHS3X78AAAAa0lEQVQI1x2KywqAIBQF+/9fiRBJr+kt9DuCgrLHpgjcaLsOwSzmcKYqzC/zpdTcNMkYzOzcKkQUAlKcS1031vVDBEe5S4kSF6hKCOC2dmnbNAzF++z9pvVJBMFMfT9J+TAje0M4iKJS+c8+mftfF4vQHtYAAAAASUVORK5CYII='); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"image5\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/bf04d0bd9d87f3262e88d137360212d3/b9e4f/img-5.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/bf04d0bd9d87f3262e88d137360212d3/cf440/img-5.png 148w,\n/static/bf04d0bd9d87f3262e88d137360212d3/d2d38/img-5.png 295w,\n/static/bf04d0bd9d87f3262e88d137360212d3/b9e4f/img-5.png 590w,\n/static/bf04d0bd9d87f3262e88d137360212d3/f9b6a/img-5.png 885w,\n/static/bf04d0bd9d87f3262e88d137360212d3/2d849/img-5.png 1180w,\n/static/bf04d0bd9d87f3262e88d137360212d3/f8b3c/img-5.png 1422w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    </p>\n<p>现在的菜单的样式是我想要的效果了。但我不喜欢这种奇怪的修改 html 的方式，也许是我的编辑器有自动格式化功能等等，上面的这种方法在我看来不是最好解决办法。</p>\n<h5>使用负的外边距</h5>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-css line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token selector\">.menu__item</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">margin-right</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> -2.6px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<p>在我的例子中，使用-2.6px 刚好可以抵消 inline 元素的空白，在实际使用中这个数值需要根据父元素上的字体大小调整。这个方法在 IE6、7 上有 Bug，如果你不需要考虑这两个浏览器的表现的话，用负外边距是一个很好的方法。</p>\n<h5>忽略元素闭合标签</h5>\n<p>使用 HTML5 的时候，你还可以忽略元素闭合标签，也能达到消除空白的目的。</p>\n<p>\n  <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/997ba970bb72db6e9032149e6152f76b/9fa53/img-6.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 590px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 44.28969359331476%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"image6\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/997ba970bb72db6e9032149e6152f76b/b9e4f/img-6.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/997ba970bb72db6e9032149e6152f76b/cf440/img-6.png 148w,\n/static/997ba970bb72db6e9032149e6152f76b/d2d38/img-6.png 295w,\n/static/997ba970bb72db6e9032149e6152f76b/b9e4f/img-6.png 590w,\n/static/997ba970bb72db6e9032149e6152f76b/9fa53/img-6.png 718w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    </p>\n<p>当然这样写和第一种方法一样怪异，故意省略闭合标签？不推荐这种方法。</p>","frontmatter":{"title":"去除inline元素之间空白的N种方法","date":" 2019年 四月 03","tags":["CSS技巧 inline元素空白"]}}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"slug":"/remove-inline-gutter/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/coerce/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"JavaScript中的类型转换（上）"}},"next":null}}